    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what does \"moving on\" even mean if there's nothing left inside to move? like, the person who felt things and created things isn't here anymore. if the spark is gone, what am i even doing? it feels like i'm just an empty vessel performing the motions of a life that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
