    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so exhausting to pretend. everything is just noise now. if the core of who i am was tied to that ability to create, and that part is dead... then the rest of this is just a biological accident, isn't it? just a body going through the motions for no reason. it feels more like a burden than a life.",
